-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Margin-- define the outer space
Padding--define the inner space --
padding:value ; top bottom left right
padding:vertical horizontal;
padding:25px 50px;
padding:10px 20px 30px;
(padding-top:10px; padding-left and right:20px; padding-bottom:30px;)
padding:10px 20px 30px 40px;
(padding-top:10px;  padding-right:20px;  padding-bottom:30px; padding-left:40px;)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
box-sizing:content-box;
box-sizing:border-box;    applicable for padding and border
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Position:
static(it is a bydefault value and top bottom are not worked in static property)
